Output demo/tui.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/wqdemo && clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 700ms
Type "waqwaq tui wiki"
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 2.6s

Down@450ms 4
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2.8s

Type "r"
Sleep 3s

Down@500ms 1
Enter
Sleep 2.6s

Type "q"
Sleep 700ms
